{"tid":1438493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（深夜奇思妙想）我知依家個運動樽頸位係咩。","createTime":"2019-08-09T18:59:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T05:09:53.000Z","uid":62011,"like":91,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"13e93d2f60088d1c3e4e75d1151d37e4861c0b74","tid":1438493,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:59:27.000Z","msg":"頭先有位巴打就今晚黃大仙一事作出黑警新策略，可以睇下呢個巴打既PO：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438314\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438314</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁其實好明顯，黑警換咗個新話事人，唔再同民眾硬碰硬，配合左膠大台同政府既經濟民生牌，目的好明顯，就係想製造內部分裂同透過其他市民無形既壓力搞散呢場運動。我呢翻說話好多人都知，我唔多講。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n唔知大家有冇一種感覺，敵人唔行動，我哋就好似唔知做咩好，好似好冇目的咁。<br />\n<br />\n呢個正係我地既樽頸位，成日畀敵人牽引住，佢做我地就做。 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n點樣去突破？ 其實好簡單，我地有我地搞，洗鬼理政府。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> 我哋既目的係要繼續維持一個失序既局面。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n失序唔等於冇秩序。 我地要話畀政府聽民間依然有一大片反對聲音，亦係同全世界講緊港共政府已經失去管治能力。直到普選來臨。<br />\n<br />\n所以我地要做既野係<br />\n1. 全面忽略政府記者會，包括黑警記者會，嗰方面就交由民間記者會搞啦。<br />\n<br />\n2 加強中外文宣，將意見繼續傳開去。 本地文宣除咗繼續表明堅持五大訴求之外，可以新增支那經濟衰落篇，解除恐共情緒。 外媒文宣可以亦要加強，可以新增女權篇，詳情參考 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1424603/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1424603/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n3 繼續參與遊行。我知道有啲遊戲黑警冇批，但張通知書形同廢紙，大家可以去行街。 行動方式好簡單：如水，唔落單，只針對政權公物。<br />\n<br />\n4 遠離一切左膠，在場見到佢，屌到佢走。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天佑吾城 光復香港"},{"pid":"cb4d45b60320f6b0e835d37be4cb79c6dfb1ee61","tid":1438493,"uid":107686,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:01:43.000Z","msg":"agger <br />\n我都出過類似既post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdabb41bd5918e51c742c14cac1f65d4fb83781b","tid":1438493,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb4d45b60320f6b0e835d37be4cb79c6dfb1ee61","tid":1438493,"uid":107686,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:01:43.000Z","msg":"agger <br />\n我都出過類似既post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:02:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b67d492ee6006425b510e149b679cf9dfbf0fa","tid":1438493,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:04:17.000Z","msg":"推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb8c6ca1564965330559a5ce6a411b83e91d153","tid":1438493,"uid":62011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:11:45.000Z","msg":"其實呢個時候，大家可以落區，連儂牆做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4687fefe0d15a7ce0225e19b4d625d700e2b7169","tid":1438493,"uid":294356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:14:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f39fabaef9c956c7ff2b8ac8930d2574bb335e93","tid":1438493,"uid":13349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:16:58.000Z","msg":"Deadline唔見左<br />\n升級唔知再點升好<br />\n<br />\n林奠八婆坐定定 笑緊我地升唔到級 又等緊我地玩火自焚"},{"pid":"d020f84cd25260dad5de30f46a865cef0b477d9b","tid":1438493,"uid":44870,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:19:37.000Z","msg":"集會遊行表達訴求 -&gt; set deadline -&gt; 行動升級 -&gt; loop<br />\n勝利formula, 一路都係靠咁樣掌握主動權, 遵從返呢個方式"},{"pid":"5db3dcb84a437ab7c17de06af0ac8a197d580b90","tid":1438493,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:20:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><em><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散 各有各做<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span></ins></em></strong><br />\n唔好意思 阻你一陣<br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人重點日程：<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>8月9-11日</strong>：機場和你飛&bull;萬人接機&bull;一連三日(1300)</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>8月10日</strong>：銀髮族遞信「900警總」&gt;「1000律政司辦公室」&gt;「1100特首辦」<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：守護孩子未來親子遊行（1030愛丁堡廣場）<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：大埔遊行（1400大埔巴士總站）（反對通知書）</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>8月11日</strong>：港島東遊行（1300維多利亞公園）<br />\n<strong>8月11日</strong>：深水埗遊行（1430楓樹街遊樂場）</span></span>"},{"pid":"b11d50da688932bfa648e20edf0699dff5bdecde","tid":1438493,"uid":31710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:25:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da746c5e05932071443408c2476ea00141978de1","tid":1438493,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:26:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa52875496a0675ec7d5b6dc465ba73dc00088a2","tid":1438493,"uid":233325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f39fabaef9c956c7ff2b8ac8930d2574bb335e93","tid":1438493,"uid":13349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:16:58.000Z","msg":"Deadline唔見左<br />\n升級唔知再點升好<br />\n<br />\n林奠八婆坐定定 笑緊我地升唔到級 又等緊我地玩火自焚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:27:44.000Z","msg":"等我地自亂陣腳<br />\n我地做得啱嘅佢冷處理<br />\n例如三罷<br />\n佢想拖，拖到我地自我毀滅"},{"pid":"87f10ab07f52007b44a37c513be00d10069597fb","tid":1438493,"uid":8745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:28:46.000Z","msg":"狗共一直不回應冷處理，都係想營造一個示威者蘑爛蓆嘅觀感<br />\n更加驚係拉得人多，街坊怕事就唔敢再出"},{"pid":"4d34abed78feeb463b13b21425f37a213f517ff1","tid":1438493,"uid":13349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa52875496a0675ec7d5b6dc465ba73dc00088a2","tid":1438493,"uid":233325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f39fabaef9c956c7ff2b8ac8930d2574bb335e93","tid":1438493,"uid":13349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:16:58.000Z","msg":"Deadline唔見左<br />\n升級唔知再點升好<br />\n<br />\n林奠八婆坐定定 笑緊我地升唔到級 又等緊我地玩火自焚